<L>__{interior the atlantis night}
<A>__{the rat and stacy are escorted by the host to a nearby table. they are given large wooden menus.}
<C>__{the rat}
<D>__{do you know what you want?}
<C>__{stacy}
<D>__{i think i will have the seafood salad special.}
<C>__{the rat}
<D>__{excellent.}
<A>__{the rat leans back in the booth. he is starting to feel in control now. then something hits him. the panic sweeps across his face. slowly, the rat reaches back to check his wallet. it's gone.}
<C>__{stacy}
<D>__{are you all right?}
<C>__{the rat}
<P>__{(weakly)}
<D>__{oh yeah.}
<A>__{cool. cool was the name of the game. stay cool.}
<C>__{the rat }
<D>__{do you mind if i excuse myself for a moment?}
